hat have trusted us"},"intro":{"eyebrow":"What we do","title":"Technology solutions for real needs.","copy":"We help companies that need to improve, build or evolve their operations with clear, functional and well-implemented tools."},"services":{"consulting":{"title":"Technology Consulting","description":"We help you evaluate, organize and implement the technology your company really needs, with a practical and grounded vision.","linkLabel":"Learn more"},"ai":{"title":"Artificial Intelligence","description":"We apply AI to automate processes, improve decisions, create assistants and generate more efficiency in your operation.","linkLabel":"Learn more"},"web":{"title":"Web Development","description":"We create websites, landing pages and platforms with a clear structure, solid design and focus on performance and conversion.","linkLabel":"Learn more"},"mobile":{"title":"Mobile Applications","description":"We design and develop intuitive and functional apps for iOS and Android, designed to grow with your business.","linkLabel":"Learn more"},"customSoftware":{"title":"Custom Software","description":"We build specific solutions for processes, operations and business models that don't fit standard tools.","linkLabel":"Learn more"},"digital":{"title":"Digital Transformation","description":"We accompany your company's technological evolution with strategy, structure and execution focused on results.","linkLabel":"Learn more"}},"cta":{"title":"Let's talk about your next project.","copy":"If you're looking for a clear, functional and well-thought-out solution, we can help you build it.","highlights":{"web":"Web & platforms","apps":"Mobile apps","ai":"Applied AI"},"primaryLabel":"Schedule a call","secondaryLabel":"Message on WhatsApp"}},"services":{"meta":{"title":"Services","description":"At Seven Siete we develop technology solutions for companies that need to move forward with more structure, efficiency and clarity."},"hero":{"eyebrow":"Services","title":"Services","description":"At Seven Siete we develop technology solutions for companies that need to move forward with more structure, efficiency and clarity. We support construction, improvement and digital evolution processes through consulting, web development, mobile applications, custom software, artificial intelligence and digital transformation. Each solution starts from a real business need and is designed to respond in a functional, scalable and strategic way."},"cards":{"consulting":{"title":"Technology Consulting","description":"We help you understand what you need, what makes sense to implement, and how to make better technology decisions for your company.","linkLabel":"Learn about consulting"},"ai":{"title":"Artificial Intelligence","description":"We apply AI to automate tasks, optimize processes, improve customer experience and drive smarter decisions.","linkLabel":"Learn about AI solutions"},"web":{"title":"Web Development","description":"We create websites and platforms with clear structure, solid design and focus on functionality, speed and conversion.","linkLabel":"Learn about web development"},"mobile":{"title":"Mobile Applications","description":"We design and develop apps for iOS and Android built for a useful and scalable mobile experience.","linkLabel":"Learn about mobile apps"},"customSoftware":{"title":"Custom Software","description":"We build tailored solutions for processes and operations that need more than an off-the-shelf tool.","linkLabel":"Learn about custom software"},"digital":{"title":"Digital Transformation","description":"We guide your company's technological evolution with strategy, structure and execution focused on results.","linkLabel":"Learn about digital transformation"}}},"contact":{"meta":{"title":"Contact","description":"Let's talk about your project and build a clear, functional and well-thought-out solution for your company."},"hero":{"eyebrow":"Contact","title":"Let's talk about your project.","description":"Reach out here or use email, phone or WhatsApp. We'll respond clearly about scope and next steps."},"form":{"sectionTitle":"Contact form","lead":"Fill in the fields and tap Send. We'll reply within 24 hours.","mailSubject":"Website inquiry — Seven Siete Company","validationRequired":"Please add at least name, email and message.","validationEmailInvalid":"Enter a valid email address.","submitLoading":"Sending...","submitSuccess":"Message sent! We'll get back to you soon.","submitError":"Could not send. Please try again or contact us directly.","nameLabel":"Name","namePlaceholder":"Name","companyLabel":"Company","companyPlaceholder":"Company (optional)","emailLabel":"Email","emailPlaceholder":"email@company.com","phoneLabel":"Phone","phonePlaceholder":"+57 300 860 0667","needLabel":"What do you need?","needPlaceholder":"Select","messageLabel":"Message","messagePlaceholder":"Brief context of the project or need.","submitLabel":"Send","needOptions":{"consulting":"Technology Consulting","ai":"Artificial Intelligence","web":"Web Development","mobile":"Mobile Applications","customSoftware":"Custom Software","digital":"Digital Transformation"}},"aside":{"eyebrow":"Other channels","title":"The same team replies via email, phone or WhatsApp.","locationLabel":"Location","locationLine":"Bogotá, Colombia","emailLabel":"Email","phoneLabel":"Phone","openEmail":"Open email","whatsapp":"WhatsApp"}},"ia":{"meta":{"title":"Artificial Intelligence","description":"We apply artificial intelligence to solve real needs within business operations."},"hero":{"eyebrow":"Artificial Intelligence","title":"Artificial Intelligence","description":"We apply artificial intelligence to solve real needs within business operations. We design solutions that automate tasks, assist processes, analyze information, optimize time and strengthen decision-making. Our approach is not based on implementing AI as a trend, but on turning it into a useful tool, integrated and oriented towards concrete results."},"highlight":{"eyebrow":"Solutions","title":"Useful AI, not decorative.","lead":"We don't talk about artificial intelligence as a trend. We treat it as a tool that must solve, simplify and deliver real value.","ctaLabel":"Talk about your project","cardsTitle":"Where we generate value","cards":{"atencion":{"title":"Customer service","description":"Assistants and chatbots that respond, schedule, filter and escalate automatically."},"operacion":{"title":"Operations","description":"Automation of internal flows, alerts and repetitive time-consuming tasks."},"documental":{"title":"Documentation","description":"Extraction, classification and document generation with minimal human intervention."},"comercial":{"title":"Sales","description":"Assistance in lead follow-up, quotes and responses to potential customers."},"datos":{"title":"Data","description":"Classification, analysis and smart summaries from unstructured information."},"tiempos":{"title":"Time","description":"Process optimization to reduce wait times, rework and bottlenecks."}}}},"consultoria":{"meta":{"title":"Technology Consulting","description":"We help companies make better technology decisions with a clear, practical vision aligned with their operations."},"hero":{"eyebrow":"Technology Consulting","title":"Technology decisions with more clarity.","description":"We help you evaluate, organize and implement the technology your company really needs, with a practical, strategic and grounded vision."},"cards":{"whatWeDo":{"title":"What we do","copy":"We analyze your current situation, understand your processes and help you define which tools, platforms or developments make the most sense for your business."},"whoFor":{"title":"Who it's for","copy":"For companies that need more clarity before investing, changing tools, building a new solution or starting a digital transformation process."}}},"webDevelopment":{"meta":{"title":"Web Development","description":"We create websites, landing pages and digital platforms designed to communicate better, project more solidity and generate results."},"hero":{"eyebrow":"Web Development","title":"Web Development","description":"We create websites, landing pages and digital platforms designed to communicate better, project more solidity and generate results. We combine design, user experience, structure and development to build clear, functional web solutions ready to grow. Each project aims to correctly represent the company's value and turn digital presence into a real tool for positioning and business."},"sectionHeading":"What we build","cards":{"corporate":{"title":"Corporate sites","copy":"Pages designed to present your brand, services and value proposition with clarity."},"landing":{"title":"Landing pages","copy":"Pages designed for campaigns, conversions and capturing opportunities."},"platform":{"title":"Web platforms","copy":"More robust solutions for users, processes, content or digital services."},"customSoftware":{"title":"Custom software","copy":"Tailored solutions for processes, operations or business models that don't fit standard tools."},"digital":{"title":"Digital transformation","copy":"We guide your company's technological evolution with strategy, structure and execution focused on results."},"consulting":{"title":"Technology consulting","copy":"We help you understand what you need, what makes sense to implement and how to make better technology decisions for your company."}},"cta":{"title":"Let's talk about your site or platform.","copy":"Tell us what you need to build, improve or launch. We'll respond clearly about scope, timelines and next steps.","highlights":{"web":"Sites & landings","consulting":"Discovery & priorities","digital":"Ready to evolve"},"primaryLabel":"Schedule a call","secondaryLabel":"Message on WhatsApp"}},"mobileApps":{"meta":{"title":"Mobile Applications (Apps)","description":"We design and develop mobile applications for companies that need to offer agile, intuitive and useful experiences on iOS and Android."},"hero":{"eyebrow":"Mobile Applications (Apps)","title":"Clear, functional apps designed to grow.","description":"We design and develop mobile applications for companies that need to offer agile, intuitive and useful experiences on iOS and Android. We build apps focused on usability, performance, scalability and integration with business processes, so they not only look good, but actually work, add value to the user and support the growth of operations."},"cards":{"service":{"title":"Service apps","copy":"For customer care, user management, information access or customer interaction."},"ops":{"title":"Operational apps","copy":"For internal processes, tracking, control and operational efficiency."},"commerce":{"title":"Commercial apps","copy":"For sales, bookings, benefits, marketplaces or branded digital experiences."}}},"customSoftware":{"meta":{"title":"Custom Software","description":"We build tailored solutions for processes and operations that need their own logic and better fit."},"hero":{"eyebrow":"Custom Software","title":"Software designed for how your operation really works.","description":"We build tailored solutions for processes, teams and business models that need something more specific than an off-the-shelf tool."},"cards":{"meaning":{"title":"What custom means","copy":"It means building a tool shaped around your operation, processes and goals—instead of forcing your company into a generic product."},"when":{"title":"When it makes sense","copy":"When the process is highly specific, when existing tools fall short or when your operation needs its own logic to run better."}}},"digitalTransformation":{"meta":{"title":"Digital Transformation","description":"We accompany companies in their digital evolution with a clear, organized and results-oriented vision."},"hero":{"eyebrow":"Digital Transformation","title":"Digital Transformation","description":"We accompany companies in their digital evolution with a clear, organized and results-oriented vision. We analyze operations, identify improvement opportunities and help implement tools, processes and solutions that make work more efficient, management clearer and growth capacity stronger. For us, digital transformation is not just changing technology, but building a better way to operate."},"cards":{"intro":{"title":"More than technology—it's evolution.","copy":"Digitally transforming a company isn't just swapping tools. It's reviewing processes, improving structures and building a clearer, more efficient way to operate."},"improve":{"title":"What can improve?","copy":"When transformation is approached with discipline, what typically improves is very tangible: clearer processes for the whole team, fewer reworks, better information flow across areas, stronger operational control and visibility, greater efficiency in how time and resources are used, and a more solid, sustainable capacity to grow."}}}},"now":"$undefined","timeZone":"America/Bogota","children":["$L25","$L26","$L27"]}]
